ruth behind an incident that got him framed while studying abroad, Xia Dong transfers from US headquarters to the Shanghai branch. In his new office, he encounters Jian Yan, his junior at school who now works as an investigator.  In the following days and nights, Xia Dong's righteousness and kindness shines through and easily helps in resolving the misunderstandings from the past. Soon after, Xia Dong and Jian Yan are conducting a background check on a company and find themselves facing repeated threats on their life after they helped Lin Jun Wen, an old classmate.","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"208883","season":1,"vote_average":8.5,"vote_count":2},"modified":"2025-03-18T20:06:16.000Z","cast":["Chu Á Văn","Vạn Thiến","Trương Manh","Viên Văn Khang","Zhang Zijian","Xue Haowen","Long Zhengxuan","Fan Shuaiqi","Jiang Fangting","Jia Yize"],"director":["Liu Yi Zhi"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chu Á Văn","name_vi":"Chu Á Văn","name_original":"Zhu Yawen","tmdb_id":1376105,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ihNzfo88inSx0TFzOgEyIiszXTD.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1376105"},{"name":"Vạn Thiến","name_vi":"Vạn Thiến","name_original":"Wan Qian","tmdb_id":1355203,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rVxTMO5xafnhbXJFXNKI1yJqcOC.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1355203"},{"name":"Trương Manh","name_vi":"Trương Manh","name_original":"Zhang Meng","tmdb_id":1612556,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1YVFLHCxI6QpGDlxx4OH4pWmbFH.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1612556"},{"name":"Viên Văn Khang","name_vi":"Viên Văn Khang","name_original":"Yuan Wenkang","tmdb_id":99690,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/auB9ZHfxdiSoJIYGu1PvblPulTm.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/99690"},{"name":"Zhang Zijian","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhang Zijian","tmdb_id":2286855,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oHcFDd3DppLyiIZagzYkLnegf52.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2286855"},{"name"